creator: HG developer
descriptionHtml:
Budget is a simple and beautiful application, it is an excellent tool for preparing family budgets so you can control your expenses and make your money pay you more.
Its main functions are:

1) It allows you to record your monthly expenses, show the total of the sum of your
     values ​​and the balance of your income.
2) Save your budgets.
3) Copy and paste your budget.
4) Lets look at your saved budgets.

Among its most important features we can mention:

1) Easy to use.
2) Totally free.
3) Occupies memory space.
4) Does not collect or share personal information.
descriptionShort: Make your money pay you, making a budget and controlling your expenses.
